Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.47,0:00:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫江戶川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.90,0:00:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是個高中生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.17,0:00:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不倖被歹徒灌下毒藥而變小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.90,0:00:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過雖然變小了 頭腦還是一樣的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.43,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個不摺不扣的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.92,0:00:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事件是在鬼屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.32,0:00:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不進去調查就無法弄清真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.10,0:00:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麽事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.62,0:00:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相永遠只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.97,0:01:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼屋殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.68,0:02:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 柯南也一起去 去消滅妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.99,0:02:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去消滅妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.43,0:02:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.81,0:02:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你找柯南去 他也一定幫不上忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.12,0:02:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是只有元太跟我兩個人的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.13,0:02:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽 你說的妖怪到底在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.23,0:02:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是四丁目的老洋房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.26,0:02:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四丁目...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.39,0:02:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.67,0:02:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說五年前那個房子的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.62,0:02:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道被誰給殺死以後 那個房子就變得很恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.59,0:03:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說的話 是一件無頭案件了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.81,0:03:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他太太跟他的兒子好像也搬走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來房子就被惡靈給佔領了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.73,0:03:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.81,0:03:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半夜總會聽見很恐怖的歎息聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.00,0:03:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心跑進去的狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔天被人發現只剩下一堆白骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.61,0:03:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且昨天晚上我也看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.21,0:03:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個房子的窗戶裏有...有鬼魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽樣 是不是開始害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.59,0:03:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西是騙人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種科學時代裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的妖怪或者是鬼魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.99,0:03:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在電視或者漫畫裏面才會出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.02,0:03:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這話什麽意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.54,0:03:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說步美在說謊是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.52,0:03:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...不是 我是說她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.91,0:03:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麽樣 既然你這麽說 那你也要一起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來證明世界上並沒有妖怪存在這個事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.39,0:03:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不來的話 小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.07,0:04:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.11,0:04:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你應該相信我說的話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.45,0:04:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.58,0:04:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 做好準備工作 準備出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.82,0:04:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.17,0:04:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大傢把帶來的東西都拿出來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.53,0:04:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我用來消滅怪物的金屬球棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.66,0:04:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我準備了肚子餓的時候的點心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.51,0:04:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爲每個人準備了手電筒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有不會迷失方嚮的指南針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 那你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.32,0:04:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我沒有準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.13,0:04:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候你怎麽死的你都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.85,0:04:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 掉以輕心的話會被做掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.46,0:04:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我努力不要死就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.13,0:04:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢夥以爲要去魔王的城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.16,0:05:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個門怎麽打不開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.32,0:05:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.46,0:05:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一陣子我先來這裏偵查的時候發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏有秘密的入口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.91,0:05:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密的入口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.71,0:05:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.45,0:05:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然藏在草叢裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.03,0:05:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要進去只有從這裏了 知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 你好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.66,0:05:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密入口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.08,0:05:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.27,0:05:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.18,0:05:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏好暗 什麽都看不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.31,0:05:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陰...陰森森的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.64,0:05:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 還是回去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.76,0:05:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 開始下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.85,0:05:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.07,0:05:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經來到這裏了 怎麽可以回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.15,0:05:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去步美一個人回去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.47,0:05:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麽行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.72,0:06:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打雷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.48,0:06:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.33,0:06:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看清楚吧 這個惡魔不過是個雕刻品而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.89,0:06:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好髒 不過跌倒而已手跟腳就都是泥土了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.53,0:06:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲長時間沒有人居住 所以地闆上到處都是灰塵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.68,0:06:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是洗臉臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.66,0:06:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好倖運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.45,0:06:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大傢這樣一起走的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.09,0:06:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像真的在執行任務的樣子 是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.47,0:06:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 我們是一個探險隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.81,0:06:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 我就是勇者了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.79,0:06:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是非常可愛的女戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.86,0:06:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是頭腦精明的魔術師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.15,0:06:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.58,0:06:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是個村民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村民的話就不算是夥伴了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.49,0:06:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 那是給我們情報的重要角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.59,0:07:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個角色最適合你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.22,0:07:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太瞧不起人了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麽意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.90,0:07:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在村民的後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你趕快去 村民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.84,0:07:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.29,0:07:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.65,0:07:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲風的關係 所以窗戶就很自然的打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.41,0:07:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看妖怪的真面目大概就是這種東西了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.62,0:07:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥 你好像是名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.42,0:07:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要去廁所一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.07,0:07:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你們在這裏等我 我馬上回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.43,0:07:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.97,0:07:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽 科學跟邏輯就是我的夥伴 再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.81,0:07:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然如此 這個房子好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.45,0:07:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前一定是個非常有錢的人住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.66,0:08:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個科學的時代裏是不可能會有那些妖魔鬼怪存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.65,0:08:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.23,0:08:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是風吹過小小的縫隙所發出來的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.75,0:08:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.07,0:08:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就看看到底是怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.07,0:08:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是...到地下室的樓梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.02,0:08:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音好像是從下面傳過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.83,0:08:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.27,0:08:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥他好慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.35,0:08:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經過來二十分鍾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.13,0:08:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢夥會不會是遇到什麽意外了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.15,0:08:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音越來越大聲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.49,0:08:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音是從那個房間裏傳來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.26,0:09:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是光彥的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.99,0:09:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這房子果然有秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.14,0:09:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥 你在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.15,0:09:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答 光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.61,0:09:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢夥到底跑哪裏去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.64,0:09:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也沒有在廁所裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.47,0:09:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個悲慘的叫聲絕對不是小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.84,0:09:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥一定發生什麽事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.44,0:09:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個到附近的房間裏躲起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.18,0:09:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在去找光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.88,0:09:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們絕對不可以到處亂跑 知道了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.65,0:09:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.76,0:09:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.87,0:09:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從發生事件之後這個房子應該就沒有人住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.58,0:09:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽水源沒有因此被停掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.30,0:09:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且窗戶開著的那個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.62,0:09:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有受到風吹雨淋的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.43,0:09:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.37,0:09:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個窗戶是最近才被打開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.03,0:09:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在不引人註意的地方制造了一個秘密入口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.31,0:10:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實有人在這棟房子裏面進進出出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.29,0:10:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的又是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.50,0:10:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這個時候媽媽她們一定在擔心我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.96,0:10:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲現在是夜深人靜的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.18,0:10:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南那個傢夥也太慢了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個不能吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.17,0:10:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥不知道到哪裏去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.43,0:10:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在一定肚子很餓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.58,0:10:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 柯南也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.41,0:10:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是他們兩個人的份 你不可以把牠吃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.48,0:10:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.83,0:10:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.84,0:10:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從那裏傳來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.48,0:10:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看一眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.11,0:10:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 柯南剛才說過不可以到處亂跑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.87,0:10:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.22,0:10:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.03,0:10:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.53,0:10:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽到處看都不像有人的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.18,0:10:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏真的沒有人在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.57,0:11:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.36,0:11:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是五年前被殺死的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.54,0:11:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片裏站在他後面的應該是太太跟他的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.89,0:11:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果那件兇殺案件並沒有抓到兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.08,0:11:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他的傢人也不曉得搬到什麽地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.46,0:11:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是元太的叫聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.14,0:11:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 不是叫他躲起來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.86,0:11:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元...元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.07,0:11:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麽了 發生什麽事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.62,0:11:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.42,0:11:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你不要嚇我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.79,0:11:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.78,0:11:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是元太的腳步聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.25,0:11:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那會是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.90,0:11:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.84,0:12:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.13,0:12:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓..不要出聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.40,0:12:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.07,0:12:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.86,0:12:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 你看清楚一點 是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.17,0:12:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在搬運著某種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.60,0:12:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.55,0:12:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.21,0:13:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.31,0:13:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近也沒有房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面就是走廊的盡頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.78,0:13:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到底消失到什麽地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.83,0:13:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我才說她是個妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.35,0:13:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地闆的灰塵有切痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.91,0:13:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我沒有猜錯的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.35,0:13:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.21,0:13:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來剛才那個傢夥在這下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.42,0:13:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 小孩子的力量拉不上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.91,0:13:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.01,0:13:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就叫做伸縮吊帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.03,0:13:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要按下按鈕 橡膠就可以自動伸縮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.34,0:13:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要綑綁犯人的時候一定會有用處的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.78,0:13:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 就用這個來試試看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個要做什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.93,0:14:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.53,0:14:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到地下室的樓梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定光彥跟元太就在這裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.46,0:14:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有光線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.91,0:14:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是牢房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.12,0:14:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽在這種地方會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.05,0:14:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好...好像有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.39,0:14:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 那個牀上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.66,0:14:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢夥是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.65,0:14:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.38,0:15:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定又做噩夢了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.74,0:15:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.82,0:15:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是都已經是五年前的事了 快把牠忘記吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.48,0:15:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲不管你再怎麽樣的痛苦 死掉的人是不會回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.54,0:15:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.33,0:15:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道她是指被殺害的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.46,0:15:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話 那兩個人是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.04,0:15:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了...你趕快吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.23,0:15:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你關在牢房裏並不是想要你痛苦的 你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.16,0:15:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昭夫 我是爲了..爲了你的將來才會這麽做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.31,0:16:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 我已經了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.67,0:16:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這棟房子的秘密還有那個時候的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.40,0:16:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得除了剛才那兩個之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.04,0:16:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還有其他的老鼠偷跑進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.14,0:16:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你們出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.01,0:16:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲起來也是沒有用的 快出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.34,0:16:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲起來也沒有用是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.32,0:16:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太 我看說的應該是你才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.34,0:16:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才在書房裏面看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.14,0:16:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前被殺的主人跟你一起所拍的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.80,0:16:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有站在照片旁邊的那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.98,0:16:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再就是在地下室裏這個面目全非的瘋漢 讓我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這個人就是你的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.24,0:17:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲眼睛下面的那顆痣完全沒有改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.09,0:17:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打從進入這棟房子裏就覺得有蹊跷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.62,0:17:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從五年前主人被殺之後他的傢人就下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.60,0:17:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人去樓空但是浴室的水龍頭裏有水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.08,0:17:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很奇怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.25,0:17:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上不會有人一直爲無人住的房子付物業費的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.49,0:17:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且在不醒目的地方做出來的出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.47,0:17:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟週圍古老的牆壁比較起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.71,0:17:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道木造的門實在是太新了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.49,0:17:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想恐怕那是命案之後才制造出來的東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.89,0:17:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲了就是希望進出這個房子不要引人註目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.17,0:17:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.25,0:17:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人住在這裏卻爲什麽要這麽做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.78,0:17:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有爲什麽非得把自己的兒子關在地下室裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.80,0:17:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個謎題從剛才你們的對話中我已經完全明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.13,0:17:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你是誰 你到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.63,0:17:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫江戶川柯南 是個偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.77,0:17:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵...偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.91,0:18:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說在這種狀況之下有兩種可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.59,0:18:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個 殺死主人的人就是太太 也就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.02,0:18:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是你把目擊一切的兒子監禁在這個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.66,0:18:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有另外一種情況就是殺死主人的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.17,0:18:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是被你關起來的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.35,0:18:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道他犯案的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.21,0:18:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定要隱藏這個事件的真相 來保護自己的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.35,0:18:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是對他而言 這樣的罪實在是太深重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.70,0:18:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從房子裏傳出來的歎息聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.15,0:18:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕就是他苦惱的歎息聲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.75,0:18:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是你的兒子爲了要減輕自己的罪孽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.58,0:18:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想要出去自首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.93,0:18:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是做母親的你卻不允許他這麽做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.07,0:18:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你知道 這一切全都是爲了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.26,0:18:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.32,0:18:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一心一意的不想讓自己的兒子成爲罪犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.69,0:18:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以選擇了不讓他走出傢門一步的隱居生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.85,0:18:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才的談話 還有你臉上的反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死你先生的人應該是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.78,0:19:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉...閉嘴 你給我閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.76,0:19:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.12,0:19:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你不要這麽做 媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如同那孩子所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.99,0:19:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯 殺死我父親的兇手就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.76,0:19:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昭夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.13,0:19:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是五年前的春天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.13,0:19:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第三次大學聯考又落榜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.44,0:19:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽 你說你又落榜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是我們傢的恥辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.84,0:19:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是敗類 你簡直就是人渣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.02,0:19:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神上已經跌到谷底的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.59,0:19:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於父親尖酸的言詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.11,0:19:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬間 我失去神智
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.71,0:19:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昭夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.59,0:19:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到我回過神來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.80,0:19:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手中握著的已經是沾滿血蹟的燭臺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.64,0:19:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地闆上躺著完全變了樣的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.65,0:20:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要擔心 媽媽會保護你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.36,0:20:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.60,0:20:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就如同你剛才所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.40,0:20:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親把現場變成是強盜犯案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.98,0:20:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把我關到這個牢房裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.03,0:20:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.86,0:20:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不想再過著這種天天夢見殺死父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.29,0:20:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怯懦的生活了 我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.66,0:20:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要贖罪才會過的輕松一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.54,0:20:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要振作起來 昭夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.36,0:20:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要忍耐 忍耐到追緝時期失效吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.23,0:20:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果...如果不說的話 不會有任何人知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.51,0:20:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.38,0:20:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這樣躲下去的話 是可以逃過警察的追捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.58,0:20:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你卻永遠逃不過你良心的譴責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.98,0:20:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.02,0:20:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你真的要讓你的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.37,0:20:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一生都背負著這麽沈重的負擔嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.04,0:21:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖的一夜過後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.88,0:21:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋房籠罩在明亮的陽光裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.11,0:21:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中途失蹤的兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.91,0:21:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在洋房外面的草叢裏面睡的正香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.31,0:21:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得他們好像是被那位太太打了蔴醉藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.49,0:21:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再從房子裏丟出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.63,0:21:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位太太跟他的兒子也在那一天嚮警方自首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.29,0:21:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有下文的殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.74,0:21:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然經過五年的時間 還是解決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.08,0:21:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然我們四個人也被傢人狠狠的教訓了一頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.95,0:21:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快讓我恢複原狀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.66,0:23:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有鬼屋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.00,0:23:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是步美發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.28,0:23:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是二丁目 叫做I藤的傢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.78,0:23:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.19,0:23:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽附近的人說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.87,0:23:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那棟陰森森的房子裏埋著妖魔鬼怪的屍骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.30,0:23:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人居住的少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.16,0:23:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也被妖魔鬼怪活活的吃下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.14,0:23:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二丁目..獨居的少年..陰森的房子..I藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.84,0:23:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真的是叫做I藤的傢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.24,0:23:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是英文的I和漢字的藤 不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.94,0:23:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 放學之後大傢在一起去突擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.25,0:23:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...等一下 那並不是I藤那是工藤 是我傢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.45,0:23:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去I藤傢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.99,0:24:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.27,0:24:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要通知警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.98,0:24:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.11,0:24:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拍攝時用過的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.59,0:24:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.60,0:24:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是電視劇拍攝的相關人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.37,0:24:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.04,0:24:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了這個案件的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.77,0:24:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.10,0:24:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視劇外景隊殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.57,0:24:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.21,0:24:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石獅子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.78,0:24:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集可是比電視劇還精彩哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.18,0:24:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.67,0:00:21.10,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相隔百年的世紀末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.76,0:00:27.31,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在應該流淚的時候我卻笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.94,0:00:39.42,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相隔太久太久的世紀末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.11,0:00:45.53,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我飛奔嚮廣闊無邊的新世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.04,0:00:52.06,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些在我孩童時代還一知半解的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.21,0:00:58.50,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在長大以後還是這樣不太明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.80,0:01:01.50,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麽了不起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.76,0:01:04.51,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更算不上是出色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.76,0:01:10.93,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所知道的只有 心裏忐忑不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.06,0:01:16.81,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那並不是答案 也並非是真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.08,0:01:22.86,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所相信的是 只有心的悸動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.12,0:01:28.36,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裏的忐忑和不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.51,0:21:53.86,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我的想象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.06,0:21:58.48,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝著涼了一半的紅茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.75,0:22:03.62,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩弄著纏繞在手指上的細繩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.40,0:22:12.62,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴著BOSSA NOVO的節奏腳歩變得輕快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.82,0:22:17.63,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謎底就在我手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.92,0:22:23.93,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 Ah- Ah- Ah-
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.11,0:22:33.77,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同的裝束 相同的地點 下週我也會在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.16,0:22:36.28,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一步接一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.46,0:22:41.20,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必對他心生厭倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.17,0:22:43.32,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個案件接一個案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.53,0:22:47.62,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎爾是否笑話我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.07,0:22:52.71,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無盡的日子以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.89,0:22:57.33,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有他在等待著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.81,0:23:01.88,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走我自己的路
